      <heading level="3">DEC-001: API Gateway 高可用方案选型</heading>
      <paragraph>**决策日期：** 2025-01-15</paragraph>
      <paragraph>**决策人：** 架构评审委员会</paragraph>
      <paragraph>**状态：** ✅ 已决策</paragraph>
      <heading level="4">背景</heading>
      <paragraph>当前 API Gateway 存在单点故障风险，一旦 Gateway 服务宕机，整个平台将无法访问。需要设计高可用方案消除此风险。</paragraph>
      <heading level="4">候选方案</heading>
      <table>
        <row>
          <cell>方案</cell>
          <cell>描述</cell>
          <cell>优点</cell>
          <cell>缺点</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**A: Nginx + Keepalived**</cell>
          <cell>Nginx 做七层负载均衡 + Keepalived 做 VIP 漂移</cell>
          <cell>成熟稳定、社区活跃、配置简单</cell>
          <cell>需要额外服务器</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**B: 云负载均衡器 (SLB/ALB)**</cell>
          <cell>使用云厂商提供的负载均衡服务</cell>
          <cell>托管服务、无需运维</cell>
          <cell>绑定云厂商、成本较高</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**C: Consul + Fabio**</cell>
          <cell>服务发现 + 动态路由</cell>
          <cell>动态感知、适合微服务</cell>
          <cell>配置复杂、额外组件</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**D: Traefik**</cell>
          <cell>原生支持 K8s 的反向代理</cell>
          <cell>K8s 集成好</cell>
          <cell>学习曲线、文档较少</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>评估维度</cell>
          <cell>权重</cell>
          <cell>Nginx+Keepalived</cell>
          <cell>云 SLB</cell>
          <cell>Consul+Fabio</cell>
          <cell>Traefik</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>可靠性</cell>
          <cell>30%</cell>
          <cell>5</cell>
          <cell>5</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>易运维性</cell>
          <cell>25%</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
          <cell>5</cell>
          <cell>2</cell>
          <cell>3</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>成本</cell>
          <cell>20%</cell>
          <cell>3</cell>
          <cell>2</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>性能</cell>
          <cell>15%</cell>
          <cell>5</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
          <cell>3</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>扩展性</cell>
          <cell>10%</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
          <cell>3</cell>
          <cell>5</cell>
          <cell>4</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**加权总分**</cell>
          <cell/>
          <cell>**4.30**</cell>
          <cell>**3.95**</cell>
          <cell>**3.50**</cell>
          <cell>**3.55**</cell>
        </row>
      </table>
      <heading level="4">评估矩阵</heading>
      <heading level="4">决策结论</heading>
      <paragraph>**选择方案 A: Nginx + Keepalived**</paragraph>
      <heading level="4">决策依据</heading>
      <paragraph>1. **成熟稳定**：Nginx 是经过大规模验证的反向代理，Keepalived 在 LVS 场景有多年应用</paragraph>
      <paragraph>2. **性能优秀**：Nginx 基于 epoll，单机可处理 10W+ 并发</paragraph>
      <paragraph>3. **成本可控**：使用开源组件，无需额外license费用</paragraph>
      <paragraph>4. **运维简单**：配置格式清晰，团队已有 Nginx 使用经验</paragraph>
      <paragraph>5. **可回滚**：方案切换对业务透明，支持快速回退</paragraph>
      <heading level="4">权衡考量</heading>
      <table>
        <row>
          <cell>考量点</cell>
          <cell>说明</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>资源投入</cell>
          <cell>需要 2 台独立服务器用于 Nginx，但可复用现有服务器</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>复杂度</cell>
          <cell>比纯云方案复杂度略高，但远低于 Consul 等服务发现方案</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>灵活性</cell>
          <cell>静态配置，变更需要修改配置并 reload；可接受</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>放弃方案</cell>
          <cell>原因</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>云 SLB</cell>
          <cell>成本较高（按流量/带宽计费），且增加云厂商绑定</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>Consul + Fabio</cell>
          <cell>引入过多组件，增加运维复杂度和故障点</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>Traefik</cell>
          <cell>与现有 Kubernetes 部署模式整合需要额外工作</cell>
        </row>
      </table>
      <heading level="4">放弃的方案</heading>
      <heading level="4">后续关注点</heading>
      <list_item>[ ] 监控 Nginx 连接数和内存使用</list_item>
      <list_item>[ ] 考虑后续迁移到更现代的方案（如 Envoy）</list_item>
      <list_item>[ ] 评估 Keepalived 单点风险（VIP 漂移依赖网络）</list_item>
