      <heading level="3">DEC-003: 数据库双写一致性方案选型</heading>
      <paragraph>**决策日期：** 2025-01-15</paragraph>
      <paragraph>**决策人：** 后端架构组 + DBA</paragraph>
      <paragraph>**状态：** ✅ 已决策</paragraph>
      <heading level="4">背景</heading>
      <paragraph>系统使用 MySQL + Redis 进行数据存储，读操作需要同时查询数据库和缓存。当前存在缓存与数据库不一致的风险。</paragraph>
      <heading level="4">候选方案</heading>
      <table>
        <row>
          <cell>方案</cell>
          <cell>描述</cell>
          <cell>一致性</cell>
          <cell>复杂度</cell>
          <cell>性能</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**A: Cache Aside**</cell>
          <cell>读时填充，写时删除缓存</cell>
          <cell>最终一致</cell>
          <cell>低</cell>
          <cell>高</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**B: 延迟双删**</cell>
          <cell>Cache Aside + 延迟再次删除</cell>
          <cell>最终一致</cell>
          <cell>中</cell>
          <cell>中</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**C: 订阅 binlog**</cell>
          <cell>监听数据库变更同步缓存</cell>
          <cell>准实时</cell>
          <cell>高</cell>
          <cell>高</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>**D: 分布式事务**</cell>
          <cell>两阶段提交/Seata</cell>
          <cell>强一致</cell>
          <cell>很高</cell>
          <cell>低</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>评估维度</cell>
          <cell>权重</cell>
          <cell>Cache Aside</cell>
          <cell>延迟双删</cell>
          <cell>binlog</cell>
          <cell>分布式事务</cell>
        </row>
        <row>
          <cell>一致性</cell>
          <cell>30%</cell>
          <cell>3</cell>
