      <heading level="4">评估矩阵</heading>
      <heading level="4">决策结论</heading>
      <paragraph>**选择方案 B: 延迟双删策略 + 补偿机制**</paragraph>
      <heading level="4">决策依据</heading>
      <paragraph>1. **团队能力**：分布式事务方案需要较深的技术积累，团队目前不具备</paragraph>
      <paragraph>2. **业务需求**：大部分场景允许短暂不一致（&lt; 1秒），无需强一致</paragraph>
      <paragraph>3. **复杂度可控**：延迟双删方案代码侵入性小，团队可自主实现</paragraph>
      <paragraph>
        4. **可监控**：可建立数据一致性检查任务，发现不一致及时修复
        <code_block/>
      </paragraph>
      <heading level="4">延迟双删实现要点</heading>
      <paragraph>┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                        延迟双删流程                                  │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>├─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                                     │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  1. 更新数据库                                                       │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│     UPDATE users SET name = 'new_name' WHERE id = 1;                │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                                     │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  2. 删除缓存（第一次）                                               │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│     DEL cache:user:1                                                 │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                                     │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  3. 延迟 100-500ms                                                  │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│     await sleep(100ms)                                              │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                                     │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  4. 删除缓存（第二次）                                               │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│     DEL cache:user:1                                                 │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                                     │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  为什么需要第二次删除？                                               │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  ┌─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  │ T1: Thread A 读取旧值                                      │   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  │ T2: Thread B 更新数据库                                    │   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  │ T3: Thread B 删除缓存                                      │   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  │ T4: Thread A 写入旧值到缓存 ← 这是问题                     │   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  │ T5: 第二次删除清理掉这个脏数据                              │   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│  └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘   │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>│                                                                     │</paragraph>
      <paragraph>
        └─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
        <code_block/>
      </paragraph>
