      <heading level="2">五、决策会议记录</heading>
      <heading level="3">2025-01-15 架构评审会议</heading>
      <paragraph>**参会人员：** 架构评审委员会</paragraph>
      <paragraph>**会议主题：** P0 风险技术方案评审</paragraph>
      <paragraph>**讨论要点：**</paragraph>
      <paragraph>1. **API Gateway 高可用**</paragraph>
      <list_item>讨论：是否使用云 SLB？</list_item>
      <list_item>结论：选择 Nginx + Keepalived，保留灵活性</list_item>
      <paragraph>2. **Kafka 可靠性**</paragraph>
      <list_item>讨论：性能 vs 可靠性如何平衡？</list_item>
      <list_item>结论：核心业务高可靠，非核心可降级</list_item>
      <paragraph>3. **双写一致性**</paragraph>
      <list_item>讨论：是否引入分布式事务？</list_item>
      <list_item>结论：当前阶段使用延迟双删，后续可演进</list_item>
      <paragraph>4. **熔断器选型**</paragraph>
      <list_item>讨论：自研 vs 开源？</list_item>
      <list_item>结论：使用 opossum，避免重复造轮子</list_item>
